---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
import { formatDate } from '../utils/formatDate.ts';

const fancySpiritsUrl = "https://fancyspirits.com";
---

<style>
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    scroll-margin-top: 80px;
  }
  .about-heading {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.6em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5em;
  }
  .about-link {
    opacity: 0.3;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1em;
    margin-left: 0.2em;
  }
  .about-heading:hover .about-link,
  .about-link:focus {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .about-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 1em;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-table th, .about-table td {
    padding: 0.75em 1em;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e2e2;
    background: none;
    font-size: 1em;
  }
  .about-table th {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .about-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* Subheading style for intro */
  .about-intro-subheading {
    font-size: 2.2em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.6em;
    margin-top: 0.2em;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5em;
  }

  /* Styled anchor links in intro */
  .about-inline-link {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1.5px dashed transparent;
    transition: border-bottom 0.18s, color 0.18s, background 0.18s;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0 .1em;
    border-radius: 0.2em;
    position: relative;
  }
  .about-inline-link:hover,
  .about-inline-link:focus {
    background: rgba(100, 132, 255, 0.10);
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid #6484ff;
    color: #6484ff;
    outline: none;
  }
</style>

<Layout
  title="About Me"
  description="Jenny — music producer, DJ, software developer, and label manager"
  pubDate={new Date('2025-10-01')}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
  <div class="about-intro-subheading">
    Hi, I’m Jenny
  </div>
  <p>
    I’m a
    <a href="#music" class="about-inline-link" aria-label="Jump to Music Producer Section">music producer</a>,
    <a href="#dj" class="about-inline-link" aria-label="Jump to DJ Section">DJ</a>,
    <a href="#dev" class="about-inline-link" aria-label="Jump to Software Developer Section">software developer</a>,
	and
	<a href="#music" class="about-inline-link" aria-label="Jump to Music Producer Section"> label manager</a>.
  </p>

  <div class="about-section" id="music">
    <div class="about-heading">
      Music Producer
    </div>
    <p>
      I love making music. That is my passion and a huge part of my life. I produce mainly Drum &amp; Bass, but I don’t limit myself to one genre. I love to push boundaries, experiment, and shape unique sounds that carry their own textures and emotions.
    </p>
    <p>
      Sound design is a form of self-expression for me. I feel it's my job to twist and shape tones until they become something new and unique. It's what I love about making music, and it's what makes my music stand out.
    </p>
    <p>
      I also help manage <a href={fancySpiritsUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fancy Spirits</a>, an independent electronic music label and community.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section" id="dj">
    <div class="about-heading">
      DJ
    </div>
    <p>
      In addition to producing music, I also love bringing my sound to the stage as a DJ. Performing live gives me the chance to share not only my own tracks, but also the music I personally connect with and enjoy.
    </p>
    <p>
      There’s something special about blending my productions with the sounds I love and then watching people react, dance, and connect to that energy.
    </p>
    <p>
      On my website, you’ll find a <a href="/" target="_self">DJ page</a> where I keep a record of previous performances and provide booking information. I’m always open to all performance opportunities, from underground club nights to big events. I bring with me a mix of passion, authenticity, and a drive to make every set unique.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section" id="dev">
    <div class="about-heading">
      Software Developer
    </div>
    <p>
      Beyond music, I’m interested in technology and software development. I do web development, desktop and mobile app development, and front-end and back-end development, as well as API and UI design.
    </p>
    <p>
      Here’s a snapshot of my current skill set:
    </p>
    <table class="about-table">
      <tr>
        <th>Area</th>
        <th>Technologies / Frameworks</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Languages</td>
        <td>C# (.NET), Python, HTML/JS/CSS</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Web</td>
        <td>Astro, FastAPI, Django</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Desktop</td>
        <td>Avalonia, MAUI, WPF</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Mobile</td>
        <td>MAUI, Avalonia</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>API/UI</td>
        <td>Design & Implementation</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <p style="font-size: 0.97em; color: #888; margin-top: 0.5em;">
      I’m always exploring new tech and creative ways to blend my love for music and software.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>